## Summary
This migration guide documents the upgrade from Flutter SDK 3.0 to 4.0, covering breaking changes including removal of `instance()` calls, Configuration object initialization, API method renames (`logEvent()` to `track()`, `uploadEvents()` to `flush()`), minimum identifier length requirements, and dependency updates for iOS 13.0+ and Browser SDK 2.

